{"word":"G3315 - μεσιτεύω - mesiteúō - mes-it-yoo'-o - Confirm","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μεσιτεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>mesiteúō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>mes-it-yoo'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Confirm"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மத்தியஸ்தராயிரு, ஸ்திரப்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to act as mediator"},{"paragraph":"2. a sponsor or surety"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3316 - μεσίτης - mesítēs - mes-ee'-tace/3316\">G3316</a>; to <i>interpose</i> (as arbiter), that is, (by implication) to <i>ratify</i> (as surety): - confirm."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3315 - μεσιτεύω - mesiteúō - mes-it-yoo'-o/3315\">G3315</a>, <a href=\"#/G3316 - μεσίτης - mesítēs - mes-ee'-tace/3316\">G3316</a>"}]}